      "side": 1,
      "message": "I wonder if we actually need to discriminate kDataIRI at all: we\u0027re going to be loading images through ResourceProvider::loadImageAsset(), and the DataURIResourceProviderProxy tries to parse the name as dataURI.\n\nSo as far as ResourceProvider is concerned, dataURI and non-local IRIs are handled via the same API.  Do we need to know the difference in SkSVG?",
      "revId": "d22ba461a5ec0598998d44b4936085f2d65b1770",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02"
    },
    {
